<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>AutoDots - Braille Translation Made Easy</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/app.css">
</head>
<body>
    <a href="#main" class="skip-link">Skip to main content</a>
    
    <main id="main">
        <section class="hero" aria-labelledby="hero-title">
            <div class="container">
                <h1 id="hero-title">Welcome to AutoDots</h1>
                <p>
                    AutoDots uses advanced AI to quickly and accurately translate between text and Braille. 
                    #if(learnMoreLink != nil):
                        <a href="#(learnMoreLink)">Learn how AutoDots can make information more accessible for you</a>
                    #else:
                        Learn how AutoDots can make information more accessible for you
                    #endif
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="features" aria-labelledby="features-title">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 id="features-title">Making Information Accessible</h2>
                <p>We understand the challenges faced by vision impaired individuals and educators in accessing information and resources. That's why we've created a tool that is:</p>
                <ul role="list">
                    <li>
                        <h3>Accurate</h3>
                        <p>Our AI technology, trained on a massive dataset of text and Braille, ensures high-quality translations, understanding context and nuances to reduce the risk of errors and misunderstandings often associated with manual transcription or outdated software.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <h3>Fast</h3>
                        <p>Get your documents translated in seconds, no matter the length. No more waiting for days or weeks for manual transcriptions.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Students can quickly convert textbooks and study materials into Braille.</li>
                            <li>Teachers can easily create accessible classroom handouts and exams.</li>
                            <li>Individuals can translate personal documents or their favorite books.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <h3>Affordable</h3>
                        <p>Being free, AutoDots offers a cost-effective alternative to expensive Braille translation software or transcription services.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <h3>Private</h3>
                        <p>Translate your documents with confidence, knowing that your information remains secure. No need to share sensitive content with third-party transcribers.</p>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="accessibility" aria-labelledby="accessibility-title">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 id="accessibility-title">Designed with Accessibility in Mind</h2>
                <p>AutoDots features a simple, intuitive interface designed with accessibility in mind. It's fully compatible with screen readers and offers keyboard navigation for a seamless experience.</p>
                <p>
                    AutoDots supports #(supportedCodes)
                    #if(specificCodesLink != nil):
                        . <a href="#(specificCodesLink)">Click here to see a full list</a>
                    #endif
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="call-to-action" aria-labelledby="cta-title">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 id="cta-title">Try AutoDots Today!</h2>
                <p>Experience the difference AutoDots can make in accessing information.</p>
                #if(ctaButton != nil):
                    <a href="#(ctaButton.link)" class="button">#(ctaButton.text)</a>
                #endif
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="commitment" aria-labelledby="commitment-title">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 id="commitment-title" class="visually-hidden">Our Commitment</h2>
                <p>We are committed to continuous improvement and welcome user feedback to ensure the highest level of accuracy.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>